    <mxCell id="legendrows" value="• Slide index / step / total&#9;—&#9;live: Yjs &quot;deck&quot; map · standalone: BroadcastChannel&#9;—&#9;presenter writes, everyone reads&#10;&#10;• Plugin shared state (poll votes, …)&#9;—&#9;Yjs &quot;plugin:&lt;id&gt;&quot; map (CRDT)&#9;—&#9;any participant writes, incl. read-only viewers; presenter-only actions gated in plugin code&#10;&#10;• Brand (data-brand)&#9;—&#9;per-window React state&#9;—&#9;local to each window&#10;&#10;• Elapsed timer&#9;—&#9;per-window React state&#9;—&#9;local to each presenter window&#10;&#10;• Participant id&#9;—&#9;sessionStorage&#9;—&#9;local (1 browser session = 1 participant)&#10;&#10;• Overlays: help / blur / overview / QR / jump&#9;—&#9;per-window React state&#9;—&#9;local UI" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=12;spacingLeft=6;" parent="1" vertex="1">
